summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain land and other property rights in Tracts 1, 2 and 3, unrecorded plat of Block 20, Denny-Fuhrman Addition to the City of Seattle; and Tracts 8, 9 and 10, Replat of Blocks 30 and 31, Lake Union Shore Lands and Replat of undivided portions of Blocks 4, 19, 20, 35, 36, 44 and 45, Denny-Fuhrman Addition, an unrecorded plat; all in City of Seattle, King County, Washington, for park, recreation and open space purposes (Olmsted-Fairview Park on Lake Union (CIP 72603)).
